document_data.name: Yellow musk extract
document_data.mainbody: '''Yellow musk extract''' was a [[drug]] that caused deep sleep for a day or more.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|4007|11}} The substance was extremely expensive and so strong that just a whiff would make a person light-headed.{{Cite digital book/Prince of Ravens/Kindle|4024|11}}
document_data.History: In the {{YearlinkName|1479}}, [[Jack Ravenwild]] purchased some yellow musk extract in [[Ravens Bluff]] and used it to knock out the slaver [[Cailek Balathorp]], known as Fetterfist.
